e144560a"},{"id":"ad047a9c86","type":"paragraph","text":"雄鸡未鸣，农夫匆匆。扛上锄头，去锄禾苗。天气炎热，饥饿腰弱。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"b826181b4a","type":"paragraph","text":"卧在树阴，疲倦×肌。忍着疲倦，去锄禾田。回家吃饭，糊糊稀饭。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"86cb70dfe1","type":"paragraph","text":"麸子窝窝，役夫难咽。血汗滴滴，灌溉禾田。粮不入×，装入国库。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"9ea616e75d","type":"paragraph","text":"农民×好，口喝黄汤。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"e3aa0d0aa7","type":"paragraph","text":" 天镇中学  ×××","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"4bfe06d5cf","type":"appellation","text":"三年级的哥哥们！","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"a37b793100","type":"paragraph","text":"我们响应你们这种正义的作法，咱们的父母已被6.25分的伙食把肚皮剥削的不成样子。再叫你们白白苦读九年书。回村受6.25分的伙食剥削是不可能的，我们首先反对这种作法。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"0c61639df1","type":"paragraph","text":" 天镇中学  ×××","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"73c38fbd5f","type":"appellation","text":"同学们！","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"94f441af4d","type":"paragraph","text":"同学们，我们不要被大话吓倒，万一问题不能很快的解决，我们也要出一出气。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"b0309e9a6b","type":"paragraph","text":"同学们，起来吧！我们不要胜利冲昏头脑，我们要有明确的政治目标。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"ea3613e93f","type":"paragraph","text":" 天镇中学  ×××","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"bedf5fcc60","type":"appellation","text":"工农生产对比","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"405a071bad","type":"paragraph","text":"工产质量高，月薪六、七十；农产质量低，月分20几，若要折起钱，不过六、七元，这样来相比，悬殊有天地，甘苦大道理，众听整疯哩，这样做下去，众人饿死哩！","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"836ea3ecff","type":"paragraph","text":" 天镇中学  ×××","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"1061ab7f8b","type":"subtitle","text":"工农生活对比","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"26bb8c9f46","type":"paragraph","text":"农民生活：","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"9b27894409","type":"paragraph","text":"农村苦实在苦，每日三餐都是糊，孩儿饿的叫爹娘，父母流泪真悲伤，","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"d55d9a275e","type":"paragraph","text":"农家到地去劳动，回家腿软路中躺，肚子饿的沽沽响，那有精神去农忙。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"10bbb7270e","type":"paragraph","text":"埋头苦干整一年，年终还是没办法，还是叫你受叫你干，要不你就当了“懒汉”。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"b4be197d46","type":"paragraph","text":"工人生活：","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"4fe3d20c99","type":"paragraph","text":"工人生活实在好，骑洋车、带手表，白面大米吃不了，饥了月饼渴了茶，","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"f90d0f58ae","type":"paragraph","text":"嘴里镶的是金牙，孩子吃的肥肥胖，穿的衣裳真漂亮，他们的生活是天堂，","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"79b66d1766","type":"paragraph","text":"工农生活来对比，真正相差天和地。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"f03bababe6","type":"paragraph","text":"天镇中学  笔名——萌发","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"6c30322acb","type":"subtitle","text":"干部农民生活的对比","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"66041a2b41","type":"paragraph","text":"黑桃虫巍巍不动，吃成肉棍；蚂蚁东跑西串，把腰饿断。","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"328421517f","type":"paragraph","text":" 天镇中学","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"12c72c9b06","type":"appellation","text":"三年级的同学们：","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"2aa46ae60a","type":"paragraph","text":"乡村的生活那么好，为什么你们不回农村生产？到了地里腰如弓、臂如弦，那多好？六分二厘五的伙食有多好。当专家、工程师多苦。工人、干部的生活最少还有三角多，饿死怎办？你们回去吧。你们为何不愿回农村呢？难道你不晓的农村生活的美满吗？你能吃的起六分二厘五的伙食吗？我看工人、干部吃的白面、大米，穿的呢子、卡叽，骑的自行车，带的手表，生活这样痛苦你们愿意吗？","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"7ad217dce5","type":"paragraph","text":" 天镇中学","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"3dd6005943","type":"appellation","text":"同学们：","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"ca4e19b004","type":"paragraph","text":"我们个人和自己的父母、姐妹都处于水深火热之中，泥泊中，黑沟里，紧着裤带睡大觉，受苦受难——我们要起来！振作身体斗争！罢课！示威！驱除那些高等奴才，寻找我们的出路，达到光明。起来吧！同学们！","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"},{"id":"ad5ade976a","type":"appellation","text":"天镇中学","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a"}],"page":{"id":"103fd45614","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"25e144560a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}